init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf said "Well, you could try making a house out of something that is not radioactive."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf said "Well, I have an idea.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You could build a house out of something that is not radioactive and then you could sell it to people who are not radioactive."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Frank said "Yeah, I know, but there's no way I could get to the other side of the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Frank looked at the wolf, still a little confused.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Frank went home and packed up his stuff.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And that's how Frank became the third richest pig in the world.
